graph LR
    LlamaStackOp[Llama Stack K8s Operator<br/>v0.3.0]

    %% External Dependencies
    LlamaStackOp -->|cluster platform| K8s[Kubernetes v1.20+]
    LlamaStackOp -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.19.4]
    LlamaStackOp -->|manifest templating| Kustomize[kustomize/kyaml v0.18.1]
    LlamaStackOp -->|image registry| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>docker.io, quay.io]
    LlamaStackOp -->|model downloads| HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub]
    LlamaStackOp -->|inference backend| InferenceProviders[Inference Providers<br/>Ollama/vLLM/TGI/Bedrock]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|optional metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|optional TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    LlamaStackOp -->|metrics integration| OpenshiftMonitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>ServiceMonitor CRD]
    LlamaStackOp -->|pod security| SCC[Security Context Constraints<br/>anyuid]

    %% Distribution-specific backends
    InferenceProviders -->|ollama distribution| Ollama[Ollama Server<br/>11434/TCP]
    InferenceProviders -->|vllm distribution| vLLM[vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP]
    InferenceProviders -->|tgi distribution| TGI[Text Generation Inference<br/>8080/TCP]
    InferenceProviders -->|bedrock distribution| Bedrock[AWS Bedrock<br/>HTTPS API]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH/RHOAI Dashboard] -.->|potential UI integration| LlamaStackOp

    %% External Services
    LlamaStackOp -->|resource management| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    PrometheusInstance[Prometheus Instance] -->|scrapes metrics| LlamaStackOp

